     C                     MOVEL'MEM5003' W0MSGD           ***************
     C                     MOVEL'MIDAS  ' W0MSGF
     C                     EXSR SRERR
     C                     END
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         R1
     C                     CLEARR#DATA
     C                     CLEARR#DEFN
     C                     CLEAR#@RDE
     C                     MOVE 'AM'      #@RDE
     C                     MOVEL'NXT BSRN'#@RDE
